Class AVFormatContext53

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bridj.NativeObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NativeObjectInterface

    public class AVFormatContext53
extends StructObject
    Mirror of the native AVFormatContext struct from the libavformat v53.x.x. For details see the Libav documentation.
    Author:
    Ondrej Perutka
